channel.description:
Coders wanted for Fatality-Server, Forums @ http://www.fatality-psc.co.nr
We need: Coders(around three would do) Idea's(Need people with good fantasy) Customer Support(For when the server is done) And: P-Mods I-Mods
If you want to co-operate, post with the following form filled in:
[b]Name: Function you want What you think you can offer Why we should pick you Tell something about yourself.. [optional] [/b]
Hope to see some reply's soon..
